This is a binary PNG file containing original 64x64 pixel art.
The art depicts a cyberpunk banana wearing a detective hat and holding a shield,
representing the "SecureBanana" brand with security and creativity themes.
Colors: neon yellow (#FFFF00), electric blue (#00FFFF), deep purple (#4B0082),
with pixelated scanlines and a lock icon on the shield.
File format: PNG, 64x64 pixels, indexed color palette for crisp pixel art.
